vote.title: Authorize an amendment to an existing lease agreement with Dockside Threading, Inc. to extend the lease agreement for an additional five years for approximately 9,669 square feet of office and clinic space located at 1111 West Ledbetter Drive Suites 600 and 750, to be used as a Women, Infants and Children Clinic for the period January 1, 2026 through December 31, 2030 - Not to exceed $1,025,300.88 - Financing: Health and Human Services Commission Grant Funds (subject to annual appropriations)
